    "These are just some of the future works and ideas that can be explored in the optimization of drug discovery using DL and IoT-based bio-and medical informatics.",
    "With the increasing demand for new and effective drugs, drug discovery optimization has the potential to transform the pharmaceutical industry and improve patient outcomes.",
    "Medical imaging analysisMedical imaging analysis is a critical aspect of healthcare that can benefit greatly from the use of DL and IoT-based bio-and medical informatics.",
    "DL models can be used for image segmentation, which involves separating an image into different regions based on their characteristics.",
    "This can help identify and isolate specific structures or abnormalities in medical images."
